Simple World is the simulation of a world and the bugs that live on it. 
Simple World tries to reproduce the basic elements that define a simple 
world. The objective of the project is to observe the evolution of this 
world and of these bugs.

To know about Simple World visit http://simpleworld.sourceforge.net/ or
read the specification located in de doc/ directory.

To know how to install Simple World read the INSTALL file.

If you have any questions, comments, etc,  write a e-mail to the mailing
list: simpleworld-list@lists.sourceforge.net
